00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:18,880
First of all, I love you both so much.
首先，我非常爱你们

7
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:22,810
-You're both so important to me. -Blah, blah, blah. Who is it?
-你们对我来说都很重要 -废话少说，到底是谁？

8
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:26,710
